      "risk": "Failover window: 5-15 seconds of unavailability during PostgreSQL primary failure",
      "severity": "medium",
      "mitigation": "Order service must implement retry with exponential backoff. Assignment requests during failover are queued, not lost. Monitor failover duration. Patroni typically achieves <10s promotion."
