      "risk": "Hot courier contention: popular couriers locked by concurrent requests causing SKIP LOCKED to cascade",
      "severity": "medium",
      "mitigation": "Randomize tie-breaking in courier selection (ORDER BY distance, random()). SKIP LOCKED inherently handles this — skipped couriers are tried by the next request. Monitor skip rates."
